Alembic migrations for CodeForge's SQLAlchemy schema.

The environment (env.py) reads the live URL from parts.world.db.engine_url() (DATABASE_URL for
PostgreSQL, else the SQLite file) and the target metadata from ArchiveBase.metadata.

  make db-migrate                                    # alembic upgrade head
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe it"   # draft the next migration

See docs/database.md.
